ose several checkboxes and select some of them within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each checkbox contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen values using this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":" (divider, read only and error mode, layout and outlined)","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"OUDSCheckboxPicker"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"images":[{"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png","type":"icon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"text":" extensions and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Components","role":"collection"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSCheckboxItem":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitem","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components with labels and icons."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identif